      "title": "General Catalyst backs two of your closest competitors",
      "body": "General Catalyst participated in Handshake's $200M Series F and in WayUp's Series A. When one investor holds two direct competitors, consolidation pressure follows - WayUp was ultimately acquired. Expect warm intros in this space to route through the same partners.",
