      "kind": "white-space",
      "title": "Nobody serves international students",
      "body": "The international-students / visa-sponsored segment has zero companies competing in it, while every other segment holds two or more. Visa complexity is the moat nobody has built: sponsorship-filtered search, CPT/OPT timelines, employer education. The gap between the direct-to-student and employer-software clusters points at the same hole.",
