      "title": "Handshake is the node everyone positions against",
      "body": "Handshake holds the highest PageRank in the landscape (0.0871) with 1,400+ university partnerships, 15M students, $200M in its latest round, and roughly 9,900 employees. Every pitch in this space will be heard as 'how is this not Handshake' - differentiation against it is mandatory, not optional.",
